---
title: Spicy Pork & Kale Soup with Ramen, Ginger, and Basil
description: Thick ramen noodles are perfect for slurping, which is exactly what you’ll be doing with this unctuous pork soup. Thai chilies pack some serious heat - be sure to add with caution!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d5c3a0f8b25efc1c8b4567.jpg
